<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>alphyriver · OPNsense plugin feed</title>
<meta name="description" content="Signed FreeBSD pkg repository bundling alphyriver's OPNsense plugins.">
<style>
  :root{
    --accent:#d4520a; --bg:#f5f6f8; --card:#ffffff; --line:#e3e6eb;
    --ink:#1b2330; --muted:#5b6675;
    --code-bg:#0d1320; --code-ink:#e7edf6; --code-cmd:#79b0ff; --code-cmt:#6b7a93;
    --ok:#1a8f4c; --radius:12px;
  }
  @media (prefers-color-scheme:dark){
    :root{
      --accent:#ff7a33; --bg:#0e1219; --card:#161d27; --line:#26313f;
      --ink:#e8edf5; --muted:#94a1b4; --ok:#43d07f;
    }
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box}
  html,body{margin:0}
  body{
    font:16px/1.6 system-ui,-apple-system,"Segoe UI",Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
    color:var(--ink); background:var(--bg); -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
  }
  .wrap{max-width:740px; margin:0 auto; padding:56px 22px 64px}
  header{display:flex; align-items:center; gap:13px; margin-bottom:6px}
  header svg{width:38px; height:38px; flex:0 0 auto; color:var(--accent)}
  header b{font-size:22px; letter-spacing:.2px}
  .pill{display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:7px; font-size:12.5px; font-weight:600;
    color:var(--accent); border:1px solid var(--accent); border-radius:999px; padding:3px 11px}
  .pill .dot{width:7px; height:7px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--ok)}
  .sub{color:var(--muted); margin:4px 0 24px; font-size:15.5px; max-width:58ch}
  .badges{display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:8px; margin-bottom:28px}
  .badge{font-size:12.5px; color:var(--muted); border:1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius:8px; padding:4px 10px; background:var(--card)}
  .badge b{color:var(--ink); font-weight:600}
  .card{background:var(--card); border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:var(--radius);
    padding:20px; margin:14px 0}
  .card h2{margin:0 0 10px; font-size:15px; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px}
  .num{width:22px; height:22px; border-radius:6px; background:var(--accent); color:#fff;
    display:grid; place-items:center; font-size:12.5px; font-weight:700; flex:0 0 auto}
  .card p{color:var(--muted); font-size:14px; margin:0 0 12px}
  pre{margin:0; background:var(--code-bg); border-radius:9px; padding:14px 16px; overflow-x:auto}
  pre code{font:13px/1.75 ui-monospace,SFMono-Regular,Menlo,Consolas,monospace;
    color:var(--code-ink); white-space:pre}
  .cmt{color:var(--code-cmt)} .cmd{color:var(--code-cmd)}
  .card code{font-family:ui-monospace,SFMono-Regular,Menlo,Consolas,monospace; font-size:.9em}
  .trust{display:flex; gap:13px; align-items:flex-start; background:var(--card);
    border:1px solid var(--line); border-left:3px solid var(--ok); border-radius:var(--radius);
    padding:16px 18px; margin:18px 0 0}
  .trust svg{width:20px; height:20px; color:var(--ok); flex:0 0 auto; margin-top:2px}
  .trust .t{font-weight:600; margin-bottom:4px; font-size:14.5px}
  .trust .fp{font:12px/1.5 ui-monospace,SFMono-Regular,Menlo,monospace; color:var(--muted); word-break:break-all}
  .links{display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:18px; margin-top:30px; font-size:14px}
  .links a{color:var(--accent); text-decoration:none}
  .links a:hover{text-decoration:underline}
  footer{margin-top:28px; padding-top:16px; border-top:1px solid var(--line);
    color:var(--muted); font-size:12.5px}
  footer a{color:var(--accent); text-decoration:none}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">

  <header>
    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"
      stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
      <rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/>
    </svg>
    <b>alphyriver plugins</b>
    <span class="pill"><span class="dot"></span>signed feed</span>
  </header>

  <p class="sub">A single signed FreeBSD pkg repository bundling alphyriver's
     OPNsense plugins. Pin the key once — every install and upgrade is verified.</p>

  <div class="badges">
    <span class="badge">packages <b>@PKG_LIST@</b></span>
    <span class="badge">ABI <b>@ABI@</b></span>
    <span class="badge">pkg signature <b>pubkey (RSA)</b></span>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2><span class="num">1</span>Trust the feed</h2>
    <p>Pin the repository config and its signing key on the firewall (run as root).</p>
    <pre><code><span class="cmt"># repo config + signing public key</span>
<span class="cmd">fetch</span> -o /usr/local/etc/pkg/repos/alphyriver.conf @PAGES_URL@/plugins.conf
<span class="cmd">fetch</span> -o /usr/local/etc/pkg/keys/alphyriver.pub  @PAGES_URL@/pkg-repo.pub</code></pre>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2><span class="num">2</span>Install</h2>
    <p>Refresh the catalogue and install. Later upgrades are just <code>pkg upgrade</code>.</p>
    <pre><code><span class="cmd">pkg</span> update   <span class="cmt"># verifies the catalogue signature against alphyriver.pub</span>
<span class="cmd">pkg</span> install @PKG_LIST@</code></pre>
  </div>

  <div class="trust">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"
      stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
      <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/>
    </svg>
    <div>
      <div class="t">RSA-signed catalogue</div>
      <div class="fp">Public key SHA-256<br>@KEY_SHA256@</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="links">
    <a href="@REPO_URL@">Source &amp; docs</a>
    <a href="@PAGES_URL@/plugins.conf">plugins.conf</a>
    <a href="@PAGES_URL@/pkg-repo.pub">pkg-repo.pub</a>
  </div>

  <footer>Built &amp; signed by CI ·
    <a href="@REPO_URL@">@REPO_SLUG@</a></footer>

</div>
</body>
</html>
